Local Char SOA_GFMD(30) : Call GFMD(SOA_GFMD) From ESSGLOB_SOA
Local Integer SOA_GWEBSERV : Call GWEBSERV(SOA_GWEBSERV) From ESSGLOB_SOA

Local Integer I
Local Date    DAT, DAT2
Local Date    DAT3
Local Integer TROUVE
Local Date    DATDEBCR
Local Char SOA_GMESSAGE(255)


#FRLAA X3-74200 2018-02-21 - START
If this.TIM <> AVOID.ACHAR
  Gosub G_C_TIM
   If SOA_GMESSAGE <> AVOID.ACHAR
    ASTATUS=fmet this.ASETERROR([L]CURPRO,mess(10,11691,1),[V]CST_AERROR)
    Return
   Endif
