#
Local Integer SOA_GWEBSERV : Call GWEBSERV(SOA_GWEBSERV) From ESSGLOB_SOA
Local Char SOA_GFONCTION : SOA_GFONCTION = "GESDCG"
Local Integer SOA_GDIMSIT : Call GDIMSIT(SOA_GDIMSIT) From ESSGLOB_SOA
Local Char RETVAL(30)(1..SOA_GDIMSIT)
Call GUSRAUZ(SOA_GFONCTION, RETVAL) From ESSGLOB_SOA

#Initialisation de la demande à "Accepté" pour les utilisateurs qui ont l'option visa
If !SOA_GWEBSERV & instr(1,RETVAL,"2") : this.STA=3 : Endif

# cannot set status here as other fields have not been defined
# for the purposes of the portal, default to 2=Request
# user can save as 1=Draft or 2=Request
#this.STA = 2

Return
